parameters:
Masamune Is this... another novel? Could it be
the continuation of the one I found before?

Masamune Why is this here... Oh, there's also a
paper with a password written on it.

Masamune Um, is the password 'Rats desert a
sinking ship.'?
That Barmila, creating such a passage.

Not only are you interfering with my plans, but
you even went as far as reporting me. You're not
even worthy of being compared to a magician.

However, I am not foolish enough to be caught
quietly by the government idiots.
I'll make use of the passage you created as well.

And if someone were to find this room, I will
share my power with them.
Read the grimoire to learn dark magic

Masamune There doesn't seem to be any
information that connects to the culprit of
Leviathan, so for now, let's keep this place a
secret.

Sub Dungeon ~The Secret Passage Connecting the
Boys' and Girls' Dormitories~ CLEAR

I decided to create a treasure vault here and
store my precious belongings.

When I graduate, I plan to take everything here
with me, but I think I'll leave behind only the
book of light magic spells.

I want to entrust this dungeon to someone with
wisdom and courage who can conquer it.

When you read this grimoire, the other grimoire
will disappear.
Learn light magic by reading the grimoire
